<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-581" src="http://bluediamondtours.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/IMG_1452-e1473632432349-225x300.jpg" alt="img_1452" width="225" height="300" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-582" src="http://bluediamondtours.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/IMG_1456-e1473632411619-225x300.jpg" alt="img_1456" width="225" height="300" />

