In order to see low-tide in Hallâ€™s Harbour, we had to leave Halifax at 6:15am â€“ not your ideal vacation start time!Â  It was worth it.Â  We saw the Bay of Fundy empty, in all its muddy gloryâ€¦.but then what to do?Â  Certainly no attractions were open that early in the morning.Â  So breakfast, but where?Â  Where else than the Big Stop in New Minas.Â  This was certainly a first for me and thoroughly enjoyed by my guests.

